Enum LikeView.HorizontalAlignment

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<LikeView.HorizontalAlignment>

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<LikeView.HorizontalAlignment>

    LikeView

    public static enum LikeView.HorizontalAlignment
extends java.lang.Enum<LikeView.HorizontalAlignment>
    Encapsulates the valid values for the facebook:horizontal_alignment attribute for a LikeView.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CENTER
      Setting the attribute to this value will center the button and auxiliary view in the parent view.
      LEFT
      Setting the attribute to this value will left-justify the button and auxiliary view in the parent view.
      RIGHT
      Setting the attribute to this value will right-justify the button and auxiliary view in the parent view.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • CENTER

        public static final LikeView.HorizontalAlignment CENTER
        Setting the attribute to this value will center the button and auxiliary view in the parent view.

        This is the default value

      • LEFT

        public static final LikeView.HorizontalAlignment LEFT
        Setting the attribute to this value will left-justify the button and auxiliary view in the parent view.

      • RIGHT

        public static final LikeView.HorizontalAlignment RIGHT
        Setting the attribute to this value will right-justify the button and auxiliary view in the parent view. If the facebook:auxiliary_view_position is set to INLINE, then the auxiliary view will be on the left of the button
